        "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\n> Patch Set 8:\n> \n> > Patch Set 7: Code-Review-1\n> > \n> > (10 comments)\n> > \n> > Unclear why DL-feeder is installed via cloudify blueprint and DL-AdminUI is done via helm?  \n> > \n> > Can one of you join the DCAE weekly meeting and clarify the deployment procedure for DL components and dependent DB? Like to know as well if any scope from DCAEGEN2-1849 will not be met for Frankfurt.\n> \n> Q1.\n> I have modified the deployment procedure. Helm and cloudify helm plugin (https://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/Cloudify+Helm+Plugin) are used to deploy both feeder and admin-UI.\n\nWe use OOM's mariadb-galera for storing DL settings. No other database dependency for F release. DCAEGEN2-1849 will be met for Frankfurt.",
