        "message": "Patch Set 15:\n\n> Patch Set 13: Code-Review-1\n> \n> (2 comments)\n> \n> minor updates needed..  Will also wait for Jack to review and provide comments if any.\n> \n> As emailed, I want to understand the reasoning behind choice of deployment of Feeder and AdminUI module via helm. Unless there is specific dependency to use helm for DL components, will prefer switching to Cloudify blueprint for next release.\n\nWe want to bootstrap the deployment process, like initial DB first then start feeder. Also, \nusing helm chart we can simplify the run.sh of each container and separate the scope of the development tasks.",
